own callbacks, but now extends `UIDialog`. The `UIDialog.show()` doesn\'t take p
arameters. The test `dialog.show()` just shows it. The callbacks are triggered b
y clicking buttons, but the tests don\'t simulate clicks.\n   - The test names a
re indeed misleading but this is not a critical issue.\n\n   - `BuildingSelector
