rSelection()` is called.\n\n9. **BuildingDetailPanel.ts**:\n   - In `show()`, `t
his.upgradeButton.setVisible(canUpgrade)` - but `UIButton` doesn\'t have a `setV
isible` method. It inherits from `Phaser.GameObjects.Container` which has `setVi
